attributes.Long form description: The student disassembles a rolling cart, first unscrews the wheels, then unscrews the middle tray brackets, unscrews the top tray brackets and removes the top tray and middle tray, then unscrews the bottom tray brackets and removes the bottom tray, unscrews the bottom bar side and removes the base frame and finally unscrews the top bar side.

attributes.Transcription: We'll now disassemble the rolling shelf from IKEA.

attributes.Action sentence: The student removes the bracket and top tray.
The student unscrews the bracket and remove the middle tray.
The student removes the bracket and bottom tray.
The student disassembles the base frame.
The student disassembles legs from the half frame.
The student disassembles the bars frames.
